abstract: In making the announcement, Intel cited stronger-than-expected demand for microprocessors and high hopes for the back-to-school shopping season.
snippet: In making the announcement, Intel cited stronger-than-expected demand for microprocessors and high hopes for the back-to-school shopping season.
lead_paragraph: The Intel Corporation raised its financial outlook for the current quarter yesterday, citing stronger-than-expected demand for microprocessors and high hopes for the back-to-school shopping season.

headline.main: Intel Raises Its Outlook; Rival Offers New Chip
